item.description: 2024 Waiting 2021 Image Processing Techniques for Chest Radiography Enhancements and Pneumonia Detection Attempts to create an expert classifier system for pneumonia diagnosis. Uses Keras framework and deployed with Flask back-end. Trained on 5000 chest X-ray images and achieves a 97% train accuracy and test accuracy of 93%. Link
